<p>Enter the street and house number.<br>
<strong>Street</strong> is a mandatory field when there is no entry under <strong>House number</strong> and <strong>Additional address information</strong>. <strong>House number</strong> is a mandatory field when there is no entry under <strong>Street</strong> and <strong>Additional address information</strong>.</p>
</div></div></td>
</tr>
