</div></div></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><div><div class="paragraph">
<p><strong>Postcode</strong><br>
<strong>Town</strong></p>
</div></div></td>
<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><div><div class="paragraph">
<p>Enter the postcode and town of the contact. This data will be used for the invoice address, for example. The order of the options <strong>Postcode</strong> and <strong>Town</strong> is reversed for certain countries, e.g. Germany.<br>
<strong>Postcode</strong> and <strong>Town</strong> are mandatory fields.</p>
</div></div></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><div><div class="paragraph">
