</div></div></td>
<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><div><div class="paragraph">
<p>Deletes the <strong>Delivery address</strong> type from the address.<br>
If the type <strong>Delivery address</strong> has not been added for the address, this option will not be visible.</p>
</div></div></td>
</tr>
