</div></div></td>
<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><div><div class="paragraph">
<p>The currently selected delivery address will be defined as primary delivery address. The ID does not change.<br>
If the <strong>Delivery address</strong> type is not selected, this option will be deactivated.<br>
If the delivery address has been defined as primary, this can be undone by clicking on <strong>Reset primary delivery address</strong>.</p>
</div></div></td>
